# External Projects - Read Only

The following directories are **reference-only** and must NEVER be modified:

- `paperclip/` — external Git repository: AI employee platform (https://github.com/yinshunyao/paperclip.git)
- `agency-agents-zh/` — external Git repository: AI agent expert team (https://github.com/yinshunyao/agency-agents-zh.git)
- `skills/` — Claude (Anthropic) skills / agent-skills reference tree; treat as upstream reference, not project-owned code
- `everything-claude-code/` — external reference project; treat as upstream reference, not project-owned code

## Rules

1. **Never create, edit, or delete** any file under `paperclip/`, `agency-agents-zh/`, `skills/`, or `everything-claude-code/`
2. **Read and search only** — use these trees as references to understand patterns, APIs, architecture, and skill formats
3. When the user asks about these projects or skills, **read and explain** the content but do not propose changes inside those directories
4. If functionality from these trees needs to be reused, **copy or adapt** the relevant code into the project's own directories (e.g. `codiiy/`, `refrence/`, or new directories at the workspace root)
